operations.query: INSERT{ ?subject ?newPredicate ?object . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  ?object . FILTER (isURI(?predicate) && STRSTARTS(str(?predicate), str(brickframe:) ) ) BIND(uri(REPLACE(str(?predicate), str(brickframe:), str(brick:) )) AS ?newPredicate) }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Temperature, brick:Chilled Discharge Water . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Chilled_Water_Discharge_Temperature . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Flow, brick:Discharge Air . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Discharge_Air_Flow . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Velocity Pressure, brick:Discharge Air . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Discharge_Air_Velocity_Pressure . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Flow, brick:Exhaust Air . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Exhaust_Air_Flow . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Flow, brick:Exhaust Air Stack . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Exhaust_Air_Stack_Flow . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Temperature, brick:Exhaust Air . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Exhaust_Air_Temperature . }
INSERT{ ?subject ?predicate brick:Velocity Pressure, brick:Exhaust Air . } WHERE { ?subject  ?predicate  brick:Exhaust_Air_Velocity_Pressure . }
